name: Intelligent Emergence [Sketch 2]
description: This piece is for #OBJKT4OBJKT 2021! Intelligent Emergence is a collaboration between myself and a Machine. Having created acrylic ink cloud artwork for 7+ years, this series will explore how a machine learning model trained on 1000+ examples of my own work can attempt to recreate, and hopefully, improve upon my own artistic output. 15 sec 1024x1024px h.264 MP4 video, looped
